<C>__{jenny}
<D>__{oh god! you're going to get us both killed. okay... in your pocket...}
<A>__{she shoves her hand into the pocket of her slacks showing him what to do.}
<C>__{jenny}
<D>__{in your pocket... pocket...}
<A>__{jenny eases in next to the pumps and stops. the attendant is already coming around the front of the car.}
