<D>__{in your pocket, please...}
<C>__{star man}
<P>__{(draws his fingers over his lips)}
<D>__{you. mouth closed.}
<C>__{jenny}
<D>__{okay.}
<A>__{the star man stuffs the gun into the left pocket of his baggy cords just as the attendant arrives at the driver's door.}
<C>__{attendant}
<D>__{morning, folks. fill her up?}
<A>__{the star man looks at jenny for help. she sweeps her fingers across her mouth to indicate her lips are sealed. the star man peeks around her at the attendant.}
<C>__{star man}
<P>__{(overly loud)}
<D>__{...gas...}
<C>__{attendant}
<D>__{you got it.}
<A>__{he leaves the window. the star man watches him until the nozzle is in the mustang, then pleased with himself, turns to jenny and lifts his face into a 'smile.'}
